  "text": "How was the Orion going to be able to act through this linkage of the Hosanna? Was this simply because of the mental distortion of the instrument at this period of time because of the uh that suggested by the music, or was it a more physical or more metaphysical link from the the time of Christ? I am Ra firstly the latter supposition is false. This entity is not linked with the entity Jehoshovah. Secondly, there is a most unique circumstance. There is an entity which has attracted the attention of an Orion, a light being.",
